“火神山功臣”火线提拔，医生妻子在一线不幸感染。
"Fire god mountain courtiers" line of fire promotion, doctor wife in the first line of unfortunate infection.
澎湃新闻                      。
The news is roaring.
澎湃新闻。
The news is roaring.
有内涵的时政新媒体。
Connotation of the new political media.
澎湃新闻记者 蒋子文此前带队参与武汉火神山医院建设工作的程曦被火线提拔为武汉建工集团（以下简称“武建集团”）副总经理。
Peng Pai journalist Jiang Zi-wen previously led the team to take part in the construction work of Wuhan Fosen Mountain Hospital was promoted to Wuhan Construction Industry Group (hereinafter referred to as "Wuhan Construction Group") deputy general manager.
据《长江日报》报道称，为鼓励干部在重大事件和困难时期敢于担当，勇于战斗，为国为民冲锋陷阵，同时，也为加强企业领导班子建设，根据程曦同志在本次防疫抗疫工作的突出成绩和其一贯表现，按照中央和省市委有关文件精神，市国资委党委及武建集团党委经过认真考察，火线提拔程曦同志为武建集团副总经理。
According to the Changjiang Daily, in order to encourage cadres to take charge, fight bravely and fight for the people during major events and difficulties, and to strengthen the building of enterprise leadership, according to the outstanding achievements and consistent performance of Comrade Cheng Xi in this epidemic prevention work, the CPSAC Party Committee and the WUBCG Party Committee have been seriously investigated.
报道披露，程曦现任武建集团下属股份公司副总经理。
Reported that Cheng Xi is now a subsidiary of WUJIANG joint-stock company deputy general manager.
1月下旬，武建集团受命对部分医院实施隔离病房改造。
In late January, WUJIANG Group was ordered to carry out the isolation ward renovation of some hospitals.
程曦于1月22日下午带领管理团队火速赶到武汉市四医院，讨论研究改造方案，组织材料及工人进场，连续奋战36小时，及时完成接诊大厅及15层楼病房改造，保证了医院在24日上午开始收治新冠肺炎患者。
On January 22 afternoon, Cheng rushed the management team to Wuhan Fourth Hospital to discuss the reform plan, organize materials and workers to enter the site, fight for 36 hours in a row, complete the renovation of the reception hall and the 15-floor ward in time to ensure that the hospital starts treating patients with pneumonia on the 24th morning.
武汉市四医院改造工作完成后，程曦又担负起武建集团火神山医院项目现场指挥部协调人和医技楼负责人的重任。
After the transformation of Wuhan four hospitals, Cheng Xi took on the task of coordinating the site command of the Fushen Mountain Hospital and the director of the hospital building.
1月23日，火神山医院正式宣布筹建，至2月2日举行交付仪式，历时10天。
On 23 January, the preparation was officially announced at Mount Huoshen Hospital, with a delivery ceremony lasting 10 days until 2 February.
10天时间，一座总建筑面积3.39万平方米，可容纳1000张床位的医院正式落成。
In 10 days, a 1,000-bed hospital with a total floor area of 33,900 square metres was inaugurated.
《长江日报》上述报道称，“作为现场总协调人，他（程曦）每天步行3万步以上，奔波于各单位，讨论确定方案、划分工作界面，有力推动了工程建设顺利推进。
"As the overall coordinator of the scene, he [Cheng Xi] walked more than 30,000 steps every day and traveled to various units to discuss and define the plan, divide the work interface, and vigorously promote the smooth progress of the project," the Changjiang Daily said.
2月1日凌晨，3间CT室的防护门因交通堵塞无法进场，他现场指挥交通，将车引导至离工地最近的地方，又组织人力搬运每扇重达300公斤的防护门，至凌晨3时所有防护门就位并立即投入安装，确保设备按期调试完毕。
In the early morning hours of 1 February, the doors of three CT rooms could not enter because of traffic jams. He directed the traffic, directed the vehicles to the nearest location from the construction site and organized the manual movement of each 300-kilogram gate. By 3 a.m., all the doors were in place and immediately put in place to ensure that the equipment was properly tuned.
医技楼是火神山医院的核心，功能复杂，土方工程量巨大，程曦严密组织施工，仅用9天时间建成，为医院早日收治病患赢得宝贵时间。
Medical technology building is the core of Fosen Mountain Hospital. It has complex function, huge amount of earthwork and strict construction in 9 days.
”对于程曦的表现，武汉市国资委予以了充分的肯定：程曦同志作为组织重点培养对象，在这次战“疫”中，勇于担当，敢于作为；冲锋在前，坚守一线；舍小家，顾大家；无惧危险，不怕苦累，经受了严峻考验，充分展示出一名共产党员应有的政治觉悟和品格情操，表现优异，成绩显著。
"To Cheng Xi's performance, Wuhan SASAC gave full affirmation: Comrade Cheng Xi, as the focus of the organization, took the lead in the battle" plague "and stood up to the frontline.
《长江日报》称他为“火神山功臣”。
The Changjiang Daily called him "a minister of the Mountain of Fire."
此外，武汉市广播电视台还透露了程曦的妻子是汉口医院的一名医生，并在抗疫一线不幸感染新冠肺炎。
In addition, Wuhan city radio and television also revealed that Cheng Xi's wife is Hankou Hospital a doctor, and in the first line of the epidemic unfortunately infected New Crown Pneumonia.
武汉市广播电视台网站“黄鹤云”报道称，“程曦同志的妻子是汉口医院的医生，自1月中旬开始就奋战在抗疫一线，没有回家，在工作中不幸被感染新冠病毒。
"Comrade Cheng Xi's wife, a doctor at Hankou Hospital, has been battling the epidemic since mid-January, did not return home and was unfortunately infected with the new crown virus at work," Wuhan Radio and TV website Huang He-yun reported
从妻子开始发烧到确诊住院，甚至到病重，程曦从未向身边同事提及此事，只是拜托妻子单位和同事照料，自己始终奋战在火神山建设工地上。
From the beginning of his wife's fever to the diagnosis of hospitalization, even serious illness, Cheng Xi has never mentioned this matter to his colleagues, just ask his wife unit and colleagues to take care of him, he has been fighting in the construction site of Mount Fire God.
从火神山医开始院建设起，程曦同志就没有回过家，一直吃住在工地，以工地为家，忘我工作，直至火神山医院建成。
From the beginning of the building of the Fire Spirit Hospital, Comrade Cheng Xi has not returned home, has been eating and living in the construction site, to the construction site, selfless work until the completion of the Mount Fire Hospital.
在医院使用进入维保阶段后，他住在办公室，每天往返于公司办公室与火神山医院之间，及时处理项目上出现的各种问题，有力保障了火神山医院的平稳运行。
After entering the maintenance phase of hospital use, he lived in his office and commuted between the office of the company and the Mount Huoshen Hospital every day to deal with the problems arising from the project in a timely manner, effectively ensuring the smooth operation of the Mount Huoshen Hospital.
”本期编辑 常琛推荐阅读。
